&lt;p&gt;As a Client Support Superhero, you will support, educate, and empower our clients and end-users so that they can be successful. You will own the client support experience and work to exceed clients&#39; expectations by genuinely caring about them, personally &amp;amp; professionally.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What Your Superpowers Are:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
